Adjust dReal 4.21.06.2 for the Guix toolchain.

Bazel 6 removed the old @bazel_tools//platforms aliases, Python 3.11 needs a
newer pybind11 than dReal 4.21.06.2 pinned, Python 3.12 removed distutils from
the default interpreter, and GCC 15 diagnoses an invalid member access in the
vendored tl::optional<T&> specialization.

